T1  - Mesoscopic imaging of glioblastomas: Are diffusion, perfusion and spectroscopic measures influenced by the radiogenetic phenotype?
A1  - Demerath T.
A1  - Simon-Gabriel C.P.
A1  - Kellner E.
A1  - Schwarzwald R.
A1  - Lange T.
A1  - Heiland D.H.
