T1  - The World Federation of Societies of Biological Psychiatry (WFSBP) guidelines for the biological treatment of bipolar disorders: Update 2010 on the treatment of acute bipolar depression
A1  - Grunze H.
A1  - Vieta E.
A1  - Goodwin G.
